flowchart TB
  User[Browser] --> CDN[CDN / WAF]
  CDN --> Web[Web Frontend]
  Web --> API[API/BFF replicas]
  API --> App[Application API]
  API --> Worker[AI & Content Workers]
  App & Worker --> PG[(Managed PostgreSQL)]
  App & Worker --> Redis[(Redis)]
  Worker --> Object[(Object Storage)]
  Worker --> Gateway[Model Gateway]
  Gateway --> Ext[External/Self-hosted Models]
  API & App & Worker & Gateway --> Obs[Logs / Metrics / Traces]
